58 37-1-12, Code of Alabama 1975, are amended to read as follows:
59 "§37-1-1
60 A commission to be known as the Public Service
61 Commission, consisting of a president and two associates who
62 shall be competent persons and qualified electors of this
63 state, is established with seven commissioners as provided
64 under Section 37-1-3."
65 "§37-1-3
66 (a)(1) The terms of office of the commissioners shall
67 be for four years; at the election to be held in the state on
